title: Sidewall, 1905–15
description: Small four-flower bouquets connected by layers of floral swag, foliate scrolls, ribbon swag, vertical lines, and twig-like swag. Ground is a light beige. Printed in greens, white, white mica, orange, grey and silver mica. Large tear.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper, mica, liquid. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-649.
